#: ../../compiler.rst:4 dfe0c3e2f4cf4292871daedec03293ed
msgid "Compiler"
msgstr "编译器"

#: ../../compiler.rst:6 70412f560d1543d0a3725c91c2a942fc
msgid ""
"The bitproto compiler generates language-specific code, which provides the "
"encode and decode api functions."
msgstr "bitproto 的编译器用来解析 bitproto 的源文件，然后生成目标语言的代码。"

#: ../../compiler.rst:12 37f426ccf0a94e0d86d616b8c511178c
msgid "Installing the compiler"
msgstr "安装编译器"

#: ../../compiler.rst:14 8f9a12c179554f7a85622adf82a24380
msgid ""
"The bitproto compiler is written in Python, and requires `Python3.7+ "
"<https://www.python.org/downloads/>`_ to work, it's best to be installed via"
" `pip <http://pip-installer.org/>`_:"
msgstr ""
"bitproto 的编译器使用 Python 编写，依赖 `Python3.7+ "
"<https://www.python.org/downloads/>`_ ，最佳的安装方式是通过 `pip <http://pip-"
"installer.org/>`_ ："

#: ../../compiler.rst:21 ae4efc4a52f94d0598b69f87ab7ccc93
msgid ""
"This will install a command named ``bitproto`` to your system, you can check"
" it's version after the installation:"
msgstr "上面的命令会安装一个叫做 ``bitproto`` 的命令行工具，你可以在安装后查看下它的版本信息："

#: ../../compiler.rst:28 90fccfc4c43f4aa6a2672d0ebd75fd0b
msgid ""
"If you're new to Python, or wish to skip a Python installation, you can "
"download the compiler from `this download link "
"<https://github.com/hit9/bitproto/releases>`_ directly, there provides the "
"prebuilt one-file executables for Mac OS, Windows and Linux, which works "
"without having to install a Python3.7+."
msgstr ""
"如果你对 Python 不熟悉，或者希望跳过 Python 安装，可以直接进 `这个下载链接 "
"<https://github.com/hit9/bitproto/releases>`_ 提供了预先打包好的单文件可执行程序，包含 Mac OS, "
"Windows 和 Linux 的三个版本，这些打包好的程序无需安装 Python3.7+ 就可以使用。"

#: ../../compiler.rst:34 68f15954315043ab8f58d49813223de5
msgid "Upgrade the compiler"
msgstr "升级编译器"

#: ../../compiler.rst:36 8ef673f4fe414df8ab6cc66220727d06
