msgstr "给目标语言生成代码："

#: ../../compiler.rst:53 67e394b9ac56457b859a31ca40ea0978
msgid ""
"It generates language-specific codes to current directory by default, to "
"specify a output directory:"
msgstr "默认地，它会把代码生成到当前目录，如果想指定一个生成目录："

#: ../../compiler.rst:60 c13449dc7c5844c9bf68bab7f1b7c74d
msgid ""
"Validates bitproto source file syntax, exits with a non-zero code if any "
"syntax wrongs:"
msgstr "仅仅检查 bitproto 的语法是否正确，如果语法错误，编译器会以一个非零的码退出："

#: ../../compiler.rst:66 14daa2fac2cc4bc2840fbb09014185cd
msgid ""
"The compiler won't generate files but only run a protocol syntax checking if"
" `-c` option is given."
msgstr "如果 ``-c`` 选项传入，编译器只做语法检查，而不会进行代码生成。"

#: ../../compiler.rst:70 c85aa668d3c74e90af43a0877f99bede
msgid ""
"By default, the compiler runs a simple protocol linter, which gives warnings"
" if the given bitproto file doesn't meet the :ref:`style-guide`, to disable "
"the linter:"
msgstr ""
"默认地，编译器会执行一个简单的协议风格检查器，以检查是否符合 bitproto 推荐的 :ref:`语法风格 <style-"
"guide>`。如果需要禁用它："

#: ../../compiler.rst:77 411be5b081374106be71713dca345373
msgid ""
"In :ref:`optimization mode <performance-optimization-mode>` (``-O``), the "
"``--endian`` option controls the host byte order targeted by the generated "
"C/C++ code, one of ``both`` (default), ``little`` or ``big``. See "
":ref:`endianness`."
msgstr ""
"在 :ref:`优化模式 <performance-optimization-mode>` (``-O``) 下，``--endian`` "
"选项用于控制生成的 C/C++ 代码所针对的宿主机字节序，可取 ``both``（默认）、``little`` 或 ``big``。参见 "
":ref:`endianness`。"
